'''Shigni''' waa [[basbaas]] shiidan (ridqan) oo lagu darsado [[cunto|cuntada]].<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://everydaylife.globalpost.com/can-serve-sweet-chili-sauce-41227.html|title = "What Can I Serve With Sweet Chili Sauce?", www.GlobalPost.com|accessdate = May 4, 2014}}</ref>
Shigniga ama basbaaska shiidan waxaa laga isticmaalaa dhamaan dunida, in kastoo lagu kala duwan yahay qaabka loo sameeyo. Tusaale ahaan, dadka [[Soomaalida]] ah waxay inta badan ka sameeyaan [[basbaas]], [[basal]], [[tamato]], [[liin dhanaan]] iyo mararka qaar oo lagu daro [[toon]]. Wadanada [[Maraykanka]] iyo [[Yurub]] waxaa caan ka ah ''"Shigniga Macaan"'' kaasi oo ah iskudarka basbaas, basal iyo geedo kale oo macaaneeya.

Guud ahaan, shigniga waxaa loo isticmaalaa in uu cuntada dhadhan fiican u sameeyo, wuxuuna ka kooban yahay in ka badan 50% basbaas.

=Khudaarta=
Khudaarta maalin walba [[dad]]ku isticmaalaan waxaa ka mid ah kuwo la kariyo iyo kuwo bisil oo sideeda lagu cuno. Isku soo wada duub hoos waxaad ku arki qaar ka mid ah guud ahaan khudaarta.
